# Normalize line endings: text files are LF in the repo and in the working tree.
# The build pipeline (scripts/build-skills.sh) parses agent/skill markdown with
# exact line matches and would mis-assemble output on CRLF, so keep these LF.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
